    "caption_text": "ZARA SRPLS – CLLCTN 16 / DROP I \n\nIn menswear, the emphasis is on fabric, detail and surface. Shirts, trousers and lightweight outer layers are refined through washed finishes, texture and check. Silhouettes remain familiar but are precisely adjusted, with trousers shaping proportion through cut and detail, and fabrication carrying variation through wash, texture and pattern. Shirts and lightweight layers introduce further nuance without disrupting the overall balance. The wardrobe extends through refinement: pieces that feel known, but register differently in wear.\n\nCreative Director: Karl Templer #karltempler\nPhotographer: Craig McDean @craigmcdeanstudio\nVideo: Ned Rogers @nedrogers \nStyling: Karl Templer #karltempler\nMake up: Mark Carrasquillo @markcarrasquillo\nHair: Lukas Tralmer @lukastralmer\nSet Designer: Gainsbury&Whiting #gainsburyandwhiting\nCasting Director: Piergiorgio @piergiorgio @dmcasting\nProduction: Gainsbury&Whiting \n\n#zara #zarasrpls",
